listing_description:
This luxurious bungalow style 5 bed 4 bath house is located in Golapganj (30 mins drive to sylhet). 
Surrounded by ponds on 3 sides and with over 6 acre space, it is the perfect place for your next vacation away from the bustling city life. It’s close proximity to Aralbill and the 3 ponds will let you fish to your hearts content. 
Stays over 1 week to get a 10% discount and stays for a month get 40% off.
A caretaker lives in a small separate house on the same property.
